{"tid":1707783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈最新處理方法","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:44:35.000Z","uid":261184,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cec01167ea44de768b59a400e5c340a757632f94","tid":1707783,"uid":261184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"如果踢落坑渠，係唔係都可以試下呢？？<br />\n<br />\n因為坑渠入面咪有水減煙降溫囉<br />\n啲煙困响坑渠入面，咪冇咁易揮發囉<br />\n就算啲煙經抗渠散，點散都係响地面，冇咁易向四周環境散發<br />\n仲可以焗死啲真嘅老鼠甴曱<br />\n目標亦明確一啲，知道將粒彈踢/掉啱方向<br />\n而且可以慳返啲水，留返啲水比大家沖下眼，啷下口，飲多兩啖都好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得呢？"},{"pid":"715eb1c69daab034f314e83c000b158274bdaf62","tid":1707783,"uid":236593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"出緊煙果陣好高溫，應該點踢好？"},{"pid":"5c3c5a5549ef4644b46733acb0910504cf28e071","tid":1707783,"uid":39331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"有沼氣 爆起上嚟手足好危險"},{"pid":"ec9aab0ae42e659c969662d029269e1a3e1758ee","tid":1707783,"uid":261184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c3c5a5549ef4644b46733acb0910504cf28e071","tid":1707783,"uid":39331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"有沼氣 爆起上嚟手足好危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"係喎，7左，對吾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}